== Configuration ==
Gentoo requires snort users to define the interface being monitored the {{Path|/etc/conf.d/snort}} configuration file.

Snort ships with an example config that must be moved and edited:
{{RootCmd|cp /etc/snort/snort.conf.distrib /etc/snort/snort.conf}}

== Boot services ==
==== OpenRC ====
To start <tt>snort</tt> at boot:
{{RootCmd|rc-update add snort default}}

To start <tt>snort</tt> immediately:
{{RootCmd|rc-service snort start}}

